        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Back boiler and fire removal where applicable</strong><p>The existing back boiler and gas fire removed as a unit. The chimney breast opening made good. All redundant pipework removed or capped. New boiler positioned in the optimal location for the property.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Full radiator set designed for each room</strong><p>We calculate the correct radiator output for every room based on size, insulation and heat loss. Every room gets the right amount of heat.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>All pipework routed and fitted</strong><p>New pipe routes planned to minimise disruption to existing decoration. We work neatly and clean up fully at the end of every working day throughout the installation.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Smart thermostat and heating controls</strong><p>New smart thermostat and programmer installed and set up. Smart controls such as Nest or Hive available on request. Required under Boiler Plus regulations for all new installations.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Magnetic system filter and inhibitor</strong><p>Magnetic filter fitted and system dosed with inhibitor to BS 7593 standard. This protects the new boiler and is a warranty condition for all major manufacturers.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Full commissioning and system balance</strong><p>Every radiator balanced individually. System pressure set and a full heating and hot water cycle run before we leave. Your new system works correctly from day one.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Gas Safe certificate and Benchmark certificate</strong><p>Both issued on the day of completion. The Gas Safe certificate is a legal requirement. The Benchmark certificate validates and registers the boiler manufacturer warranty.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>12-month workmanship guarantee</strong><p>All St Helens installations carry a 12-month workmanship guarantee. If anything fails as a result of our installation work, we return and resolve it at no cost.</p></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
